{"tid":2107595,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港股擴大跌幅至逾500點    陳茂波稱資金持續流入　港區國安法可維持投資環境穩定","createTime":"2020-07-14T03:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T04:02:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"19b2c080855941c8279c9377c70853ec6942895a","tid":2107595,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:45:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537604-20200714.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537604-20200714.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCnxq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=05cb56d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537604-20200714.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=80e5b0cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537604-20200714.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n港股跌幅擴大至逾500點，恒指報25270點，下跌501點，跌幅近2%。<br />\n<br />\n吉利汽車回落近6%，騰訊跌3.7%。<br />\n<br />\n瑞聲科技跌4%，舜宇光學科技跌逾3%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537609-20200714.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537609-20200714.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCnxq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=884e6e3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537609-20200714.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0da455a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537609-20200714.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波表示，有說法指《港區國安法》影響投資信心，導致資金外流，他認為這些言論都是妄顧事實的主觀猜測。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波出席一個「一國兩制」與基本法的網上論壇時說，客觀數據顯示，自從今年4月以來，港元匯率持續靠近7.7港元兌1美元的強方區域，並且多次觸及強方兌換保證，金管局至今已接到超過總值1千億港元的美元資金流入，香港的利率亦持續偏低，港股走趨轉強，單日成交量曾超過2千億元，反映香港不但沒有資金外流，反而持續有資金流入，強調《港區國安法》可以維持香港投資環境穩定。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波說，過去一年香港社會承受了暴力打擊，亦出現分離主義，突顯了國家安全的缺口。《港區國安法》堵塞了相關的法律漏洞，從制度上為國家安全提供保障，避免香港被利用作分裂國家的工具，亦讓香港回復安全穩定，令「一國兩制」行穩致遠。"},{"pid":"c70a550cdc8a20ea552a65765834bb5c8f4de793","tid":2107595,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:46:29.000Z","msg":"老強搬錢走"},{"pid":"4c0b4e40bd802b58fe5e0ed6cd6bb36f84a3ca95","tid":2107595,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:47:02.000Z","msg":"托囉你咪<br />\n<br />\n膠下你有幾多錢托"},{"pid":"68c6276327b6b5d670e1e9a3920a8e0a18be8738","tid":2107595,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"音樂椅遊戲結束了"},{"pid":"7c3dcb2e61a21bff52c6fd7c7e32a94291769f23","tid":2107595,"uid":119756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:48:50.000Z","msg":"係囉！叫大陸救市啦"},{"pid":"df8a51a02d9eb429e6ba720321960889d6f53f24","tid":2107595,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c7b808b42532721a23fd46af552c9ee45ada2de","tid":2107595,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:54:57.000Z","msg":"北水南調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Thx, China<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670fb4e0182c949b9aaa1a2cc5e4b49411fb29de","tid":2107595,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:57:57.000Z","msg":"香港政府升又贏~跌又贏~"},{"pid":"475e29b99a062fb33bf714355e3ec637a561c4c2","tid":2107595,"uid":323443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T04:02:17.000Z","msg":"繼續托到2047<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}